  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/740340/extras/198b9347b8cabc297b56715028b6767f.avif?t=1772669111\" width=250 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dive into NeuroMatrix, a gripping first-person escape room adventure within the twisted, ever-evolving mind of an A.I. Minimalist, liminal space, atmospheric exploration, science-fiction, action shooter and puzzles. 15 levels and more to come!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>It’s just me, pouring my soul into this vision, crafting one level at a time. Want to back an indie dev’s grind? Grab NeuroMatrix and take on the challenge!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>If you like the project and just want to help the development of the game, consider a simple donation with Paypal by using the \"<u>Visit the website</u>\" link on the right >></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your support keeps this dream alive, thanks for stepping into my world!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/740340/extras/198b9347b8cabc297b56715028b6767f.avif?t=1772669111\" width=250 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dive into NeuroMatrix, a gripping first-person escape room adventure within the twisted, ever-evolving mind of an A.I. Minimalist, liminal space, atmospheric exploration, science-fiction, action shooter and puzzles. 15 levels and more to come!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>It’s just me, pouring my soul into this vision, crafting one level at a time. Want to back an indie dev’s grind? Grab NeuroMatrix and take on the challenge!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>If you like the project and just want to help the development of the game, consider a simple donation with Paypal by using the \"<u>Visit the website</u>\" link on the right >></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your support keeps this dream alive, thanks for stepping into my world!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
